title: Alison Balsom - Caprice
description:
Young classical trumpet soloist Alison Balsom performs Paganini's Caprice with the Gothemberg Symphony Orchestra. Other selections include Rachmaninoff's Vocalise, the Nocturne from Tomasi's Trumpet Concerto, Seven Spanish Songs by Falla and others. A varied and virtuoso performance. 

All MP3 files are fully tagged. (Titles are in the the tags.) Encoded in highest quality VBR with Fraunhaufer II MP3 Pro codec.
